In "''[[Pulse-21|The World of 0 and 1]]''", [[Tailmon]] explained that some Digimon were able to draw from the power that slept within their Digicore, including [[Wizarmon (Dreamers)|Wizarmon]], who could use it for the legendary electric attack, {{ATO|Bolt Break}}. A [[Greymon]] was used for her example.

[[Pulsemon (Dreamers)|Pal]] has a special Digicore, which allows him to manipulate electricity at will after evolving into [[Bulkmon]] and use {{ATO|Core Electrical Fist}}. This was first shown in "''[[Pulse-23|A Dream to Evolve]]''".
