The '''Human Spirit of Fire''' (炎のヒューマンスピリット ''Honō no Hyūman Supiritto''), also known as the '''Spirit of Fire H''' (炎のスピリットH ''Honō no Supiritto Eichi'') is one of the twenty [[Legendary Spirits]]. It contains the power of [[Ancient Greymon]] of the [[Warrior Ten]], and allows its user to evolve into the Human Form [[Hybrid]] [[Digimon (species)|Digimon]] [[Agnimon]].

=Appearances=
==Anime==
==={{hdr|Digimon Frontier}}===
According to [[Baromon]], the Human Spirit of Fire is one of the Spirits that was given to [[Ofanimon (Frontier)|Ofanimon]] after the Warrior Ten defeated [[Lucemon (Frontier)|Lucemon]].{{rfe|DF|38|Endless Death Match! The Prelude of Lucemon's Revival}} When [[Cherubimon (Frontier)|Cherubimon]] turned evil and began his war, the Human Spirit of Fire was hidden in [[Fire Terminal]].

The Human Spirit of Fire is the first of the Spirits to be found by the [[Chosen Child]]ren when Ofanimon calls them to the Digital World. When [[Cerberumon]] attacks Fire Terminal on Cherubimon's orders to find the Spirit, the Spirit reacts to [[Kanbara Takuya]]'s [[D-Scanner]], chooses him as its user, and reveals itself. Takuya scans the Spirit and uses it to [[Evolution#Digimon Frontier|Spirit Evolve]] into [[Agnimon]] and fight Cerberumon.{{rfe|DF|01|The Legendary Warrior! Agnimon of Flame}}

Takuya continues to use the Spirit throughout the series. During his fight with [[Mercuremon (Frontier)|Mercuremon]] in his [[Black Seraphimon]] form, [[Seraphimon (Frontier)|Seraphimon]]'s [[DigiTama]] releases some of its power to enable Takuya to combine the Human Spirit with the [[Beast Spirit of Fire]] to become [[Aldamon]].{{rfe|DF|28|Takuya's Fusion Evolution, Aldamon's Explosive Attack!}}

During the battle against Cherubimon at the [[Venus Rose]], Cherubimon subdues Takuya and takes his D-Scanner, along with all the Spirits in it, but [[Ofanimon (Frontier)|Ofanimon]] steals all of the D-Scanners and Spirits back under the pretense of purifying Cherubimon and returns them to the Chosen Children. When Ofanimon upgrades Takuya's D-Scanner, he becomes able to use this Spirit with nine other Spirits to Hyper Spirit Evolve into [[Kaiser Greymon]].{{rfe|DF|35|Spirits Become One! Takuya and Kouji's Ultimate Evolution!}}

In their last battles with Lucemon, the Chosen Children gain the ability to combine all twenty Spirits, including the Human Spirit of Fire, to become [[Susanoomon]].{{rfe|DF|48|Light and Darkness are One! Kouichi's Last Wish}}

