In ''[[Digimon Story: Lost Evolution]]'', this Spirit is called by a different name: 火のスピリット (''Hi no supiritto'').

==={{hdr|Digimon Story: Cyber Sleuth Hacker's Memory}}===
The Human Spirit of Fire is an item that, once the player obtains it, allows either of the compatible Child Digimon ([[Agumon]] and [[Guilmon]]) to evolve into Agnimon, as long as they also meet the other evolution requirements. The item is not consumed in the evolution, so Agnimon can be evolved into any number of times. Agnimon and [[Wolfmon]] drop the Human Spirit of Flame, along with the [[Human Spirit of Light]], when the player defeats them in the Cyber Crimes Investigation Unit Server in Chapter 8.

