|pe=A God Man Digimon that contains the data of a {{w|Chang'e|Chinese moon goddess}}. It is a calm and beautiful Digimon that usually lives in solitude on its ship known as the {{EQ|Kōkankyū|Moon Palace}}, which resembles the moon. Although it seldom has the chance to show it off, Jougamon is a master of {{w|Chinese martial arts|Ch'uan Fa}}, and uses its specialty kicking techniques and high mobility to make sport of the opponent in battle. When faced with a powerful opponent, it summons its huge-bladed, crescent-shaped weapon called "{{EQ|w=Moon Rabbit|Gyokuto|Jade Rabbit}}", and fights boldly while wielding it freely. The way it fights with its Ch'uan Fa and {{EQ|Gyokuto|Jade Rabbit}} is both feared and lauded as being chilling and beautiful, like the moonlight in winter.{{br}}Its Special Moves are jumping up while equipping {{EQ|Gyokuto|Jade Rabbit}} to its foot, and then delivering a {{w|flying kick}} ({{AT|Tsui Getsu Shō|Falling Moon Rush}}), and making {{EQ|Gyokuto|Jade Rabbit}} spin rapidly to send out slashes into its surroundings ({{AT|Gabi Seppa|Crescent Moon Slash Wave}}). Its "{{AT|Taiin Kōkō|Lunar Radiance}}", which emits light from a raised-up {{EQ|Gyokuto|Jade Rabbit}} to heal its comrades, boasts of unrivaled healing power, but since it often spends its time alone, it has few opportunities to use it.
|pj=中国に伝わる月の女神のデータを内包した神人型デジモン。普段は{{EQK|広寒宮（こうかんきゅう）}}という月のような見た目の船で孤独に暮らす、物静かで美しいデジモンだ。見せる機会は少ないが拳法の達人で、戦闘となれば得意の蹴り技と高い機動力で相手を翻弄する。強大な敵を前にすると「{{EQK|玉兎（ぎょくと）}}」という三日月状の巨大な刃の武器を召喚し自在に操り果敢に戦う。拳法と「{{EQK|玉兎}}」で戦う姿は、冬の月光のように寒々しくも美しいと、恐れられると同時に称えられている。<br>　必殺技は、跳び上がると同時に「{{EQK|玉兎}}」を足へと装着し、そのまま跳び蹴りを放つ『{{ATK|墜月衝（ついげつしょう）}}』と、「{{EQK|玉兎}}」を高速回転させて周囲へ斬撃を飛ばす『{{ATK|蛾眉截波（がびせっぱ）}}』。掲げた「{{EQK|玉兎}}」から光を放ち仲間を癒す『{{ATK|太陰皓光（たいいんこうこう）}}』は強力無比な治癒力を誇るが、孤独に過ごすことが多いため使用する機会は少ない。
