|p=Digimon Reference Book
|e=Some say that whenever someone looks up at the moonlit night, and occasionally sees a door leading to another horizon open up, it is because Kaguyamon is crying. Residing in the beautiful bamboo grove regions spread across the [[Digital World: Shambala|Eastern Digital World]], Kaguyamon has been strongly influenced by the data of a princess mentioned in a {{w|The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter|tale}} passed down in Japan since ancient times.{{br}}It has a nature that loves peace and tranquility above all else, and is responsible for protecting the mountains that make up most of the Eastern Digital World. It has the ability to open gates to faraway places or [[Digital World (concept)|Digital World]]s of other dimensions, and transports its targets, enveloped in light, via bamboo that appears at their destinations. Since it dispatches many of its subordinate Digimon to locations where strange phenomena have occurred, bamboo groves are said to form at sites where gates have been opened.{{br}}Its bamboo tube-like device has a mechanism that emits psychic waves, and utilizing its telekinesis grants it high mobility and the ability to fly. Because it can easily control powerful, vast amounts of psychic waves, there are times when it will use its telekinesis to deal with problems itself that its subordinate Digimon were unable to handle.{{br}}Its Special Moves are using its telekinesis to forcibly disarm the enemy, and firing a volley of psychic bullets to annihilate its surroundings ({{AT|Taketori Monogatari|Tale of Military Capture}}), and causing meteorites summoned from another space to rain down directly above enemy forces ({{AT|Tsukiyo no Mukae|Moonlight Reception}}).
|j=ふと月夜を見上げたとき、ときおり別の地平へと通ずる扉が開かれるのは、カグヤモンが泣いているからだと誰かが言った。東方のデジタルワールドに広がる美しい竹林地帯に棲まうカグヤモンは、日本に古来から伝わる物語に記された姫のデータに強く影響を受けている。<br>　静寂と平和をこよなく愛する性格で、東方のデジタルワールドのほとんどを占める山々の守護を担っている。遠くの場所や別次元のデジタルワールドへと続くゲートを開く能力を持っており、光で包んだ対象が目的地に出現する竹を通じて転送される。異変が起きた場所に配下のデジモンを複数送り出すため、ゲートが開かれた跡地には竹林が形成されるという。<br>　竹筒のような装置は念波を放出する仕組みを持っており、念動力を活用することで高い機動力・飛行能力を備えている。強力かつ膨大な量の念波をたやすく操るため、配下のデジモンで対応できなかった問題には自ら念動力で手を下すこともある。<br>　必殺技は、念動力で敵の武装を強制解除させ、念波の弾丸で周囲一帯を殲滅する一斉射撃『{{ATK|武獲物語（たけとりものがたり）}}』と、敵戦力の真上に別の空間から喚び出した隕石を降り注ぐ『{{ATK|月夜之迎（つきよのむかえ）}}』。
|u=kaguyamon
|ety={{JP}} {{ETY|Kaguya}}<br>
From {{ETY|{{FGU|Kaguya}}-hime}} {{ETYK|{{FGM|かぐや}}姫}}, the main character of the Japanese folklore ''{{w|The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter}}''.
