|p=Digimon Reference Book
|e=A Dragon Man Digimon with delicate scales and fins resembling a dress. It has the ability to synthesize various types of poison, such as those that paralyze the enemy, or those that melt substances. Making poisons that gradually shorten the opponent's life is Lamiamon's number one specialty, and it is said that this is because it takes pleasure in watching its opponents suffer. The umbrella it carries has the function of storing the poisons it synthesizes.{{br}}Due to it being well-versed in poisons, and the extent of its knowledge, it is capable of breaking down all kinds of viruses. Because of this, it seems that there are occasions when Lamiamon will detoxify other Digimon in exchange for a hefty reward.{{br}}Its Special Move is opening up its umbrella, coating it with poison, and attacking while scattering poison to contaminate its surroundings ({{AT|Venobrella}}). It shoots a raging stream of concentrated poison from the tip of its umbrella ({{AT|Splash Toxin}}) at opponents it deems unworthy of the amusement of watching suffer, killing them instantly.
|j=ドレスのように可憐な鱗やヒレを持つ竜人型デジモン。敵を麻痺させる毒や物質を融解させる毒など、様々な種類の毒を生成する能力を持っている。もっとも得意とするのは、徐々に相手の命を削る毒であり、これはラミアモンが相手の苦しむ様を楽しむためだといわれている。手にした傘は生成した毒をストックする役割を持つ。<br>　毒に対する造詣が深く、その知識の高さからあらゆるウィルスの類を分解することが出来る。そのため、ラミアモンは莫大な報酬を受け取る代わりに他のデジモンの解毒を請け負うこともあるらしい。<br>　必殺技は傘を広げて毒でコーティングし、攻撃を弾きつつ毒を撒き散らして周囲を汚染する『{{ATK|ヴェノブレラ}}』。苦しむ姿を見て楽しむに値しない相手には、傘の先端から濃縮した毒の激流『{{ATK|スプラッシュトキシン}}』を放ち、即座に死に至らしめる。
|u=lamiamon
|ety={{GRE}} {{ETY|Lamia}} <br>
{{noun}} From {{ETY|{{w|Lamia}}}} (Ancient Greek: Λάμια ''Lámia''), was a child-eating monster in {{w|Greek mythology}}.
