|dref2=<ref name=DRB-EN/>{{note|While this Digimon is correctly called ''Crimson Mode'' in its page name in the English version of the [[Digimon Reference Book]], its Profile instead calls it ''Wrath Mode''. No such contradiction is present in its Japanese Profile.|n=wrath}}
|ol={{ZHO}} 威灵兽：深红形态{{DD|na|nazhamon_crimson}} <small>/</small> 威灵兽CM{{ref|''[[Digimon New Century]]''}}<small> - From ''"{{ETY|Wēilíng Xiǎnhè Dàjiāngjūn}}<small>(威灵显赫大将军)</small>"'', which is a title given for ''"{{w|Nezha}}<small>(哪吒)</small>"'' in {{w|Taoism}}.</small><br>{{CHI}} 哪吒獸：真紅蓮型態{{DD|na|nazhamon_crimson}}
|image=Nezhamon crimson.jpg
|imagesize=320x320
|l1=Ultimate
